      • getClosestSupportableUnit

        private bwapi.Unit getClosestSupportableUnit()
        Function for finding the closest Unit whose UnitType matches one of the listed ones in the PlayerUnitTerran_ScienceVessel's List of supportable UnitTypes. The List defined in this Class determines the order in which the different UnitTypes are searched through. The UnitTypes at the beginning of the List are preferred while the ones at the end are considered last.
        Returns:
        the closest Unit that the executing Unit can support.

      • getDefensiveMatrixTarget

        private bwapi.Unit getDefensiveMatrixTarget(PlayerUnit playerUnit)
        Function for finding the closest Unit of the ones being currently around the PlayerUnitTerran_ScienceVessel that is a viable target for the Defensive_Matrix ability of the vessel.
        Parameters:
        playerUnit - the Unit that is executing the Action.
        Returns:
        the closest Unit that the executing Unit can / should use the ability on.

      • isInDanger

        private boolean isInDanger(bwapi.Unit unit)
        Function for testing if a Unit is in danger. This includes being attacked by an enemy Unit and having less hit points than a set percentage of the max ones left.
        Parameters:
        unit - the Unit that is going to be tested.
        Returns:
        true if the Unit is in danger, false if not.
